{"tid":2400140,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【明寸隊友】ERROR三子打邊爐唔預保錡 阿Dee爆粗193喝住嗌唔好","createTime":"2021-02-08T16:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T17:08:36.000Z","uid":226955,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"78657b3251ca758326e6e5574d270578fc0ff605","tid":2400140,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1995078/即時-娛樂-明寸隊友-ERROR三子打邊爐唔預保錡-阿Dee爆粗193喝住嗌唔好?fbclid=IwAR0-vSOLkdXyb5-HiF2lX3S6g5THIJuH5cPCllPeuuB7Pssdt8glAWGhaOc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1995078%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E6%98%8E%E5%AF%B8%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%8B-ERROR%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%90%E6%89%93%E9%82%8A%E7%88%90%E5%94%94%E9%A0%90%E4%BF%9D%E9%8C%A1-%E9%98%BFDee%E7%88%86%E7%B2%97193%E5%96%9D%E4%BD%8F%E5%97%8C%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0-vSOLkdXyb5-HiF2lX3S6g5THIJuH5cPCllPeuuB7Pssdt8glAWGhaOc&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=726ae8c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1995078%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E6%98%8E%E5%AF%B8%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%8B-ERROR%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%90%E6%89%93%E9%82%8A%E7%88%90%E5%94%94%E9%A0%90%E4%BF%9D%E9%8C%A1-%E9%98%BFDee%E7%88%86%E7%B2%97193%E5%96%9D%E4%BD%8F%E5%97%8C%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0-vSOLkdXyb5-HiF2lX3S6g5THIJuH5cPCllPeuuB7Pssdt8glAWGhaOc&h=265a11d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1995078/即時-娛樂-明寸隊友-ERROR三子打邊爐唔預保錡-阿Dee爆粗193喝住嗌唔好?fbclid=IwAR0-vSOLkdXyb5-HiF2lX3S6g5THIJuH5cPCllPeuuB7Pssdt8glAWGhaOc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKCuhyr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKCuhyr.jpg&h=f30eea83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肥仔享同隊友193及阿Dee打邊爐的片段，近期被負面新聞纏身的保錡則未有現身。<br />\n<br />\n男子組合ERROR成員保錡自從被爆與性感女神張沛樂（沙律）拍拖後，接連爆出負面新聞，繼被指控偷食後，又在網上公然爆粗鬧網民，形象全毀，不少網民擔心保錡會影響ERROR發展，要求他退出ERROR。今日ERROR隊長肥仔在ig分享與隊友193及阿Dee打邊爐的片段，爆粗爆到走晒Fans的保錡就冇影。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9D1S6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9D1S6Y.jpg&h=90fb1c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為太好味，阿Dee忍唔住爆粗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ipXrr5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ipXrr5.jpg&h=0c9c5b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n保錡自12月與性感女神張沛樂（沙律）公開戀情後，接連爆出負面新聞。<br />\n<br />\n片段可見ERROR三子食長腳蟹食得津津有味，期間食住蟹肉的阿Dee突然爆出一句：「好X肥美。」隊友193即大聲喝住，「唔好講粗口」，負責拍片的女友人亦警告他不要講粗口。肥仔更要求友人刪除了這段影片。之後阿Dee便改口笑稱:「我成功食咗梁業喇!」明寸隊友保錡爆粗鬧網民一事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVNetFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTVNetFA.jpg&h=8dbadb7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿Dee日前在IG透露ERROR即將推出新歌，更公開了自己在新歌MV中的造型照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCuo6so.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCuo6so.jpg&h=ab403fee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n保錡早前在網上直播公然爆粗鬧網民。"},{"pid":"5b34707e5c521f62cc2b31cc9cbb19866bc60d49","tid":2400140,"uid":224533,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"稍為有啲良心都應該同佢割席啦"},{"pid":"70527f24be9bbb357f324a31293de518f01843ba","tid":2400140,"uid":60074,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T17:21:42.000Z","msg":"隻保錡自動消失啦<br />\nError 得返三個真心冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fb8bf7f07c03a0189231b21d17db5099617f8a","tid":2400140,"uid":389390,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5b34707e5c521f62cc2b31cc9cbb19866bc60d49","tid":2400140,"uid":224533,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"稍為有啲良心都應該同佢割席啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"不過近幾日 Error仲有一齊拍嘢<br />\n所以好難講真定假割席<br />\nBtw早排pk生日 193同dee gor都有同佢慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji